OL,6,FTwenty thousand children aged three to
OL,7,F13 are to be screened for type 1
OL,8,Fdiabetes as part of a new trial that
OL,9,Fcould "transform the way the condition
OL,10,Fis identified and managed" at its
OL,11,Fearliest stages.
OL,13,FThe Early Surveillance for Autoimmune
OL,14,FDiabetes (Elsa) study, launching on
OL,15,FMonday for World Diabetes Day, will
OL,16,Fscreen blood to identify children that
OL,17,Fare likely to develop diabetes,
OL,18,Fallowing earlier diagnosis.
